---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Social & Economic Impact - AI for Humanity" description="Understanding AI's implications for labor markets, equity, access, and economic development while ensuring benefits are shared broadly across communities and regions.">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900 via-purple-700 to-purple-600 text-white overflow-hidden">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-10"></div>
		<div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24">
			<div class="text-center">
				<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
					<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Social & Economic Impact</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-purple-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					AI's transformative effects on labor markets, equity, access to technology, and economic development 
					require inclusive policies and global collaboration to ensure benefits reach all communities.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Overview -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">Reshaping Societies and Economies</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
				AI's social and economic impact is reshaping societies and economies, influencing labor markets, 
				equity, and access to technology worldwide. While AI offers opportunities to augment human capabilities 
				and drive innovation, it also presents challenges such as job displacement, unequal access, and ethical concerns.
			</p>
			<div class="bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-400 p-6">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-2">Key Insight</h3>
				<p class="text-purple-700">
					Addressing these impacts requires inclusive policies, global collaboration, and a focus on ensuring 
					AI benefits are shared broadly across different communities and regions.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Three Pillars of Impact -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-12 text-center">Three Critical Areas of Impact</h2>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<!-- Labor -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2-2v2m8 0H8m8 0v2m-8-2v2m0 0v2h8V8m-8 0H4m16 0v8a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V8"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Labor Impact</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
						Addressing AI's impact on labor is necessary to ensure social and economic systems 
						endure and flourish through AI transformation.
					</p>
					<div class="space-y-3">
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
								<strong>Varied Impact:</strong> Some labor replaced, most augmented, new opportunities created
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
								<strong>Skills Investment:</strong> Academia, civil society, public and private coordination needed
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
								<strong>Gradual Adoption:</strong> Rapid adoption should not be necessary to survive disruption
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Equity -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197m13.5-9a2.5 2.5 0 11-5 0 2.5 2.5 0 015 0z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Equity & Inclusion</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
						Ensuring equity in both the design and deployment of AI systems and tools is 
						essential for AI to truly work for humanity.
					</p>
					<div class="space-y-3">
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
								<strong>Cross-jurisdictional:</strong> Global commitment needed to define and drive AI equity
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
								<strong>Open Source:</strong> Enables representative systems built by diverse stakeholders
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
								<strong>Impact Assessment:</strong> Focus on equity to demonstrate deployment effects
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Access -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 7a2 2 0 012 2m4 0a6 6 0 01-7.743 5.743L11 17H9v2H7v2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2.586a1 1 0 01.293-.707l5.964-5.964A6 6 0 1121 9z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Access & Accessibility</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
						Access and accessibility are necessary to build better AI systems and ensure 
						equitable participation in the AI ecosystem.
					</p>
					<div class="space-y-3">
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
								<strong>Global Disparities:</strong> Address gaps in infrastructure, data, talent, and governance
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
								<strong>Interoperability:</strong> Global standards vital for safe, trustworthy, and equitable systems
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
								<strong>Future Tech Stacks:</strong> Cooperative cross-sector investment needed
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Global South Challenges -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-12 text-center">Challenges for the Global South</h2>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">The Access Challenge</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-700 mb-6">
						Advancing open AI standards requires sustained effort, with a growing emphasis on inclusive, 
						context-aware development—particularly for the Global South. Key challenges include balancing 
						openness with proprietary control and ensuring equity, access, and accountability.
					</p>
					
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<div class="bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-4">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">Recurring Tensions</h4>
							<p class="text-red-700 text-sm">
								There's a recurring tension between openness and proprietary lock-in, especially 
								impacting regions with limited resources and infrastructure.
							</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-lg p-4">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-2">Crisis as Catalyst</h4>
							<p class="text-amber-700 text-sm">
								Past crises (e.g., 2008 financial crisis) created momentum for open solutions; 
								today's humanitarian funding crises could play a similar role.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-blue-50 rounded-xl p-8">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Requirements for AI Benefit</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-700 mb-6">
						To benefit from AI, the Global South needs access to data, talent, and digital power. 
						Context-specific AI models are essential—many current models exclude non-dominant 
						languages and data contexts.
					</p>
					
					<div class="space-y-3">
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
							<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-purple-500 rounded-full"></div>
							<span class="text-slate-700">Access to high-quality data and datasets</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
							<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-purple-500 rounded-full"></div>
							<span class="text-slate-700">Local talent development and retention</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
							<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-purple-500 rounded-full"></div>
							<span class="text-slate-700">Digital infrastructure and computing power</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
							<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-purple-500 rounded-full"></div>
							<span class="text-slate-700">Context-relevant AI models and applications</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-purple-200">
						<p class="text-sm text-purple-700 font-medium">
							"Inclusion should not be an afterthought but part of system design from the start"
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Climate & Finance Impact -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-12 text-center">AI's Climate-Related Financial Impact</h2>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
				<!-- Why It Matters -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Why Responsible AI Matters for Finance</h3>
					<div class="space-y-3">
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-700">Climate risk is a technology challenge - and AI accelerates that</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-700">AI is also a labor, trust, and equity challenge</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-700">Without governance, AI undermines social stability</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- If Guided Correctly -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">If Guided Correctly, AI Can</h3>
					<div class="space-y-3">
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-700">Optimize complex systems</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-700">Accelerate clean tech innovation</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-700">Provide better data, faster</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-2">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
							<p class="text-sm text-slate-700">Enhance decision intelligence</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- OS-Climate -->
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">OS-Climate Solution</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-700 text-sm mb-4">
						Building the plumbing - data pipelines, open models, regulatory-grade tooling - 
						that everyone can plug into for climate-aligned finance.
					</p>
					<div class="space-y-2">
						<div class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
							Pre-competitive & collaborative
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
							Radically transparent
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
							Open infrastructure for ESG
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-blue-50 rounded-xl p-8">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">The Financial System's Role</h3>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					<div>
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Key Lever for Change</h4>
						<p class="text-slate-700 text-sm mb-4">
							Finance is seen as a key lever for systemic change (e.g., green tech adoption, climate insurance). 
							Insurance and investment institutions can enable or stall innovation depending on whether they underwrite risk.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Information Asymmetries</h4>
						<p class="text-slate-700 text-sm mb-4">
							Governments often lack the data access and technical expertise that banks and private firms have—creating 
							asymmetries. Open systems offer a way to reduce information monopolies.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Collaboration Requirements -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">Building Trust Through Collaboration</h2>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
				<!-- Skepticism vs. Benefits -->
				<div class="bg-red-50 rounded-xl p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-red-800 mb-4">Collaboration Challenges</h3>
					<p class="text-red-700 mb-4">
						There's skepticism about collaboration between grassroots/open-source developers and institutions 
						(e.g., banks) because their goals may be at odds with each other.
					</p>
					<div class="bg-red-100 rounded-lg p-4">
						<p class="text-red-700 text-sm">
							<strong>Reality Check:</strong> Engagement must acknowledge each side's incentives—collaboration 
							is rarely purely altruistic.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Open Source Benefits -->
				<div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-6">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-800 mb-4">Open Source Advantages</h3>
					<p class="text-emerald-700 mb-4">
						The argument in favor of collaboration is that open-source ensures transparency, equal access 
						to code, and accountability—an antidote to power asymmetries.
					</p>
					<div class="space-y-2">
						<div class="flex items-center text-sm text-emerald-700">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
							Transparency and equal access
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center text-sm text-emerald-700">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
							Accountability mechanisms
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center text-sm text-emerald-700">
							<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
							Reduced power asymmetries
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-8 bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-400 p-6">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-2">Essential: Consent and Data Revocability</h3>
				<p class="text-purple-700">
					In open collaborative efforts, consent and data revocability must be built into the system—especially 
					for vulnerable users or communities. Trust frameworks are essential for enabling safe participation 
					in shared data infrastructures.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Call to Action -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-purple-900 text-white">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Build an Equitable AI Future</h2>
			<p class="text-xl text-purple-100 mb-8">
				Join the global effort to ensure AI's benefits reach all communities through inclusive design, 
				open collaboration, and responsible governance.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
				<a href="https://globaldigitalcollaboration.groups.io/g/GDC-AIForHumanity-SocialEconImpact" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
					Join Social Impact Discussion
				</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/os-climate/OS-Climate-Community-Hub#readme" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-purple-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
					Explore OS-Climate
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>